{"tid":1508360,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"前線：屌鳩你班和理非港豬 回帰大陸啦","createTime":"2019-08-26T13:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T14:52:06.000Z","uid":144696,"like":18,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"55bd31fc645bcc956b323d4008be4d82ddddd764","tid":1508360,"uid":144696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:32:01.000Z","msg":"屌我分化撚又好 開戰狗又好<br />\n我自己有發夢過 有外宣過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線俾人打 俾人捉 食tg 幫你地搵咁撚多核彈 出到國際既得零零星星幾個<br />\n［核彈整合］[推上熱門］10幾個核彈，唔用就笨柒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1504990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1504990</a><br />\n<br />\n我屌哂你地老母 開Twitter好難咩？ Retweet又好難咩？？？<br />\n平時啲post 外國人佔左一半有多 得番10-20k <br />\n好 當全部都係你地 說好的和理非不割席？ 說好的100萬和理非？<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 人呢？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n成日喺ig story分享俾朋友 屌下狗全家就當自己文宣咗？你而家當自己係明星定係youtuber?<br />\n咁撚多真嘢唔撚用 㩜炒巴既post又唔夠人支持 要咁快用到假嘢？<br />\n核彈都唔割已成共識，咁大家接唔接受到有利己方既假新聞？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507798</a><br />\n<br />\n上網睇下直播員 連登做下旁述員 就當自己參與咗？<br />\n連登全體心聲：感謝勇武<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1504748\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1504748</a><br />\n<br />\n出來遊行既200萬人 100萬人 <br />\n留守既得2000人 都唔知有冇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己見到有一小撮朋友出去 一大半朋友出去睇戲食飯拍拖 痛心到不得了<br />\n<br />\n我自己都覺得自己咩都做唔到 好廢<br />\n<br />\n個個都覺得自己前途好重要 無可限量<br />\n你有冇諗過前線有女仔有小朋友 仲有唔少好靚 你係唔係男人？係連登打一句有事我養你 就叫幫手？<br />\n我唔係企係最前 都覺得自己冇資格講呢句說話<br />\n<br />\n你有冇諗過有人有國藉 有人有能力移民 有人已經前途無量都企出來幫你班港豬？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但你又有冇嘗試過幫手？<br />\n如果和理非唔進化 但多一排 前線俾人捉到差唔多 就係咁先 <br />\n理撚得你和理非 準備奶共啦 <br />\n<br />\n1.機場<br />\n2.Twitter <br />\n3.留守：<br />\n因為少人留守 前線先俾人叫暴徒 啲狗先覺得自己係啱既<br />\n你試下20萬人留守？<br />\n夠1萬已經偷笑 夠10萬我裸跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好心你地生性啦 發完夢心力交瘁 仲要出長文屌鳩醒你哋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641f90dc0f6ba7ae4307fa2bffb4714378cc7e31","tid":1508360,"uid":144696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:34:50.000Z","msg":"[嘈夠啦！正經野無人做！]連登幾多人有Twitter ac? 有核彈無人禁個制有撚用？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508171</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4dfc9b520dd072c9420c3023d0e3e53ac3d7aba3","tid":1508360,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:36:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"54afa5fd03d5837f46c12cee5e5f24fe74588cb7","tid":1508360,"uid":18772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:41:41.000Z","msg":"回<span style=\"color: red;\">帰</span>"},{"pid":"1d73ee6c52e57d675f61c4c605e058820226c104","tid":1508360,"uid":144696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"54afa5fd03d5837f46c12cee5e5f24fe74588cb7","tid":1508360,"uid":18772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:41:41.000Z","msg":"回<span style=\"color: red;\">帰</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry巴打"},{"pid":"01576525d8a77f5002c01d323889f3403eef4fe3","tid":1508360,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5ZOzj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5ZOzj.gif&h=0e4bb77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2